WEBVTT

00:15:29.100 --> 00:15:30.244
će naći bolje načine

00:15:30.244 --> 00:15:31.388
koji će uključivati,

00:15:31.388 --> 00:15:32.533
verovatno kombinaciju

00:15:32.533 --> 00:15:34.267
svega ovoga.

00:15:34.267 --> 00:15:36.133
Hvala.

00:15:36.133 --> 00:15:38.270
(Aplauz)

00:15:38.270 --> 00:15:43.829
Bruno Đuzani: Tomas Piketi. Hvala.

00:15:43.829 --> 00:15:46.078
Tomase, želim da Vam postavim
nekoliko pitanja,

00:15:46.078 --> 00:15:49.567
jer je impresivno kako baratate
informacijama koje imate,

00:15:49.567 --> 00:15:53.361
ali Vi zapravo hoćete da kažete

00:15:53.361 --> 00:15:54.934
da je rast gomilanja imovine

00:15:54.934 --> 00:15:56.858
samo jedna tendencija kapitalizma,

00:15:56.858 --> 00:16:00.396
i ako je ostavimo samoj sebi,